## PPUD

Public Protection Unit Database (PPUD) is the current authority system for case management of offenders serving life sentences and indeterminate sentences of imprisonment for public protection, recalled offenders and offenders who are restricted patients. Developed by [Lumen](https://www.lumen.com/en-us/home.html), a project is underway to rework this service - see [here](https://dsdmoj.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PR/pages/4234379302/Business+Overview)

## OASys

Offender Assessment System (OASys) manages the operational database used to assess the risks and needs of eligible offenders in prisons and probation trusts.

Also see the [Assess Risks and Needs](https://dsdmoj.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ARN/overview?homepageId=2358771974) project.